k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p><span lang=3D"PT-BR" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Raffaella,<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please find my responses and details pr=
ovided below in green for easy reference.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-co=
lor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Attached are the document=
s which have been produced in relation to your claim to date.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-co=
lor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">In reading both of your r=
ecent emails I can identify the areas of your claim that you have requested=
 further clarification on. I have
 reasoned that your enquiries are centered around 4 general areas of the cl=
aim response. As follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li style=3D"color:#4EA72E;margin-left:12.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo16"><sp=
an style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#3=
B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%"><span style=3D"color:windowtext=
">Forensic testing of resulting damages
 and testing methodology with respect to clearances.<o:p></o:p></span></spa=
n></li><li style=3D"color:#4EA72E;margin-left:12.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo=
16"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-c=
olor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%"><span style=3D"color:win=
dowtext">Structural assessment of resulting damages
 and testing methodology with respect to clearances.<o:p></o:p></span></spa=
n></li><li style=3D"color:#4EA72E;margin-left:12.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo=
16"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-c=
olor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%"><span style=3D"color:win=
dowtext">Consenting and Compliance regarding
 the repairs required.<o:p></o:p></span></span></li><li style=3D"color:#4EA=
72E;margin-left:12.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo16"><span style=3D"font-size:1=
1.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfil=
l-fill-alpha:100.0%"><span style=3D"color:windowtext">Policy Response [ The=
 specific coverage
 and benefits which can be applied to your claim by your insurer ]<o:p></o:=
p></span></span></li><li style=3D"color:#4EA72E;margin-left:12.0pt;mso-list=
:l8 level1 lfo16"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-t=
extfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%"><span styl=
e=3D"color:windowtext">Privacy requests.
<o:p></o:p></span></span></li></ol>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-co=
lor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">The only instrument avail=
able to Tower Insurance is to appoint professional service providers to att=
end, discuss, assess, test and report
 on the areas and the aspects of the property which you have suggested wher=
e they may be resulting damage.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill=
-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">When referring to the =
5 different fields above; the responses can be provided by the following 5 =
entities:<o:p></o:p></span></u></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-co=
lor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">1&amp;2 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Tower Insurance will request that a CPEng and a Forensic Sc=
ientist are to attend, discuss, assess, test and report on the
 areas and the aspects of the property which you have requested or suggeste=
d where they may be resulting damage.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-co=
lor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">3 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ASURNZ to provide consenting and co=
mpliance advice.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-co=
lor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">4 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - For Policy Response =E2=80=93 Kelly=
 Mason &amp; Bryan Strong would provide response and discussion on this asp=
ect of your claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-co=
lor:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">5 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - For your privacy request our claims=
 department is currently compiling the requested documents.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill=
-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">In summary the propose=
d site meeting/assessment attendees to assess and provide adequate response=
s to your enquires would be:<o:p></o:p></span></u></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso=
-style-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Br=
yan Strong</span></b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-styl=
e-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">
 =E2=80=93 Senior Manager Property Assessing<o:p></o:p></span></p>
