<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso=
-style-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">St=
ephen Walker</span></b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-st=
yle-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">
 =E2=80=93 Technical Building Consultant. ASURNZ.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso=
-style-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Wa=
rwick Banks</span></b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-sty=
le-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">
 =E2=80=93 Associate Structural Engineer. CPEng<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso=
-style-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Al=
exandra Dalzell</span></b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso=
