<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;color:#3B7D23;mso-st=
yle-textfill-fill-color:#3B7D23;mso-style-textfill-fill-alpha:100.0%">Thank=
 you for considering my response. The above proposal is the best that I can=
