<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hi Rafaella,<o:p></=
o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you for your =
emails dated 12 &amp; 17 September 2025. In response, and as previously ind=
icated, we are keen to meet with you at 23 Mays Road, Devonport on
<u>Friday September 2025 at 1:00pm</u>. Our goal of this meeting is to walk=
 side by side with you through your home, so that you can talk us through y=
our concerns and to ensure that we are capturing all information relevant t=
o your Tower Insurance House policy
 claim # C90306048 and ensuring that all your concerns are resolved. <o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I will endeavor to =
gather the supporting information that you have referred to in your previou=
s emails and provide that to you well ahead of this site meeting so we can =
discuss and review together. I will
 also send through, and agenda based on your email, prior to the meeting, s=
o that all parties can address and progress the individual subjects raise. =
&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">In further response=
 to your email, I would like to advise you of the people from Tower who wil=
l be attending this meeting:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
