meet current Code requirements (structure/barriers)
 and whether producer statements or LBP supervision are proposed.<o:p></o:p=
></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l14 level1 lfo1"><sp=
an style=3D"font-size:10.0pt">Deck: current scope proposes only a partial d=
eck replacement, although Grant has recently indicated the full deck would =
be rebuilt. Could you please explain how a patch repair
