/span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l14 level1 lfo1"><span=
 style=3D"font-size:10.0pt">How each relevant element=E2=80=94whether inclu=
ded in the current scope or currently omitted (e.g., walls/ceilings, framin=
g, insulation, services, roof-edge components, masonry/brickwork,
 kitchen, basement storage areas, deck, roof-space plant)=E2=80=94will be a=
ddressed to achieve the policy standard of reinstatement =E2=80=9Creasonabl=
y equivalent to when new=E2=80=9D across appearance, size, functionality, i=
ntegrity and relative quality; and, for any omitted element,
