></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l14 level1 lfo=
1"><span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt">Kitchen: why no kitchen works are inclu=
ded despite the earlier heavy smoke staining (later cleaned by David, engag=
ed by Tower). Please provide the evidence used to exclude
